net/mlx5: Use ida_alloc_range() instead of ida_simple_alloc()

ida_simple_alloc() and remove functions are deprecated.
Related change:
commit 3264ceec8f17 ("lib/idr.c: document that ida_simple_{get,remove}() are deprecated")

